Table A: Running EQ6 from EQ3/6-V8.0a (R43a) for PC
Description= 'Solubility of minerals in the system MgSO4-H2SO4-H2O'
This is part of the EQ3/6 Test Case Library
Add H2SO4 to epsomite saturated water to compute the solubility of
minerals in the system MgSO4-H2SO4-H2O. Note that some epsomite is also
added to the system early in the run. The initial mass ratio of epsomite
to solution is not identical to that in the version 7 line equivalent of
this input file. Thus; some details in the results will vary. The important
compositional relationships should remain the same.
